y":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T20:11:07.000Z","msg":"希望你地早日搵返開始嘅愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T20:32:23.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ae8cfb3a2b9a3ca781c77e4b7b4e34b6d5d1d0","tid":696593,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T20:38:19.000Z","msg":"屌你，講中哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8904d51807d10941247ac28005ea7bf63e360e","tid":696593,"uid":19567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T00:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n依種感覺好絕望 好絕望<br />\n<br />\n一般閑聊嘅談笑風生無曬<br />\n以往係社交平台嘅相片無曬<br />\n<br />\n後來 講嘢態度唔似從前<br />\n後來 Ig嘅caption慢慢變到灰暗 有關我嘅相片亦慢慢消失<br />\n<br />\n可能再後來 已讀不回 唔care咁<br />\n可能再後來 ig status已經唔關我事 相片變成個人生活記錄<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n回憶慢慢退色 心中已唔會有任何波動<br />\n<br />\n見住過往辛苦盡力經營嘅感情被自己一手破壞<br />\n慢慢枯萎而無能為力 亦怨恨自己嘅無能<br />\n幾多積極幾多開心嘅偽裝都係呃自己 呃自己並唔在乎<br />\n鬼叫自己就係咁唔坦率嘅人 連自己都呃<br />\n<br />\n可恨 可憎..."},{"pid":"eecec0ca65919a513bd97cb25a0967a83b11a2ad","tid":696593,"uid":11963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2ae8cfb3a2b9a3ca781c77e4b7b4e34b6d5d1d0","tid":696593,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T20:38:19.000Z","msg":"屌你，講中哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T00:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}